   The  Game  Waking  up  cold  and alone,  you've  been  'Kidnapped'.
   Traverse through a terrifying two hundred year old manor, dark damp
   caves, an eerie forest full of wildlife and more.  Kidnapped  is  a
   psychological  story-driven adventure  horror game,  with  a  great
   emphasis on exploration, puzzle solving and combat. A  large number
   of  objects  in the  game world  can be  interacted  with,  whether
   examined, used, or picked up.

   For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/382300/
